import React from "react";
import 'bootstrap/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css';
import {Card, CardBody} from 'reactstrap';

function Post()
{
    return(
        <>
        <>
  <Card className="my-2">
    <CardImg
      alt="Card image cap"
      src="https://picsum.photos/900/180"
      style={{
        height: 180
      }}
      top
      width="100%"
    />
    <CardBody>
      <CardTitle tag="h5">
        Card Title
      </CardTitle>
      <CardText>
        This is a wider card with supporting text below as a natural lead-in to additional content. This content is a little bit longer.
      </CardText>
      <CardText>
        <small className="text-muted">
          Last updated 3 mins ago
        </small>
      </CardText>
    </CardBody>
  </Card>
  <Card className="my-2">
    <CardBody>
      <CardTitle tag="h5">
        Card Title
      </CardTitle>
      <CardText>
        This is a wider card with supporting text below as a natural lead-in to additional content. This content is a little bit longer.
      </CardText>
      <CardText>
        <small className="text-muted">
          Last updated 3 mins ago
        </small>
      </CardText>
    </CardBody>
    <CardImg
      alt="Card image cap"
      bottom
      src="https://picsum.photos/900/180"
      style={{
        height: 180
      }}
      width="100%"
    />
  </Card>
</>
        </>
    )
}

export default Post;
